  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Open the site's own status board.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 1.628,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "One location, pulled onto one screen.",
      "startS": 1.628,
      "endS": 3.661,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "The trail up top shows you drilled in from the network center,",
      "startS": 3.661,
      "endS": 7.187,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "and the back link runs you straight back there when you're done.",
      "startS": 7.187,
      "endS": 10.443,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "Start with the header.",
      "startS": 10.88,
      "endS": 11.89,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "Site, status, address, the account it belongs to, and who manages it, all in a single strip.",
      "startS": 12.68,
      "endS": 14.905,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "The sync time tells you how current this is.",
      "startS": 15.189,
      "endS": 16.544,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "Right now it's a couple of minutes old, and the status reads critical.",
      "startS": 16.856,
      "endS": 25.977,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "Three buttons sit to the right.",
      "startS": 26.468,
      "endS": 28.042,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "These are your fast responses: open a job, ping the account manager,",
      "startS": 28.491,
      "endS": 31.429,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "or push the site up the priority list.",
      "startS": 31.782,
      "endS": 35.255,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Each one kicks off something real, so today we read them and keep our hands off.",
      "startS": 35.963,
      "endS": 40.081,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "Now the numbers.",
      "startS": 40.64,
      "endS": 41.541,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "Six tiles across, and every one carries its own yardstick.",
      "startS": 42.177,
      "endS": 45.947,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "Washes and revenue today against their averages.",
      "startS": 46.391,
      "endS": 49.004,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "Wait time and service level against target.",
      "startS": 49.558,
      "endS": 51.82,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "And the count of open incidents, which is where the trouble surfaces.",
      "startS": 52.338,
      "endS": 55.851,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "You read today's figure next to its benchmark, without doing the math yourself.",
      "startS": 56.563,
      "endS": 60.48,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "Middle of the page, the equipment panel.",
      "startS": 60.88,
      "endS": 63.096,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "Eight units at this wash, one card each,",
      "startS": 63.72,
      "endS": 66.424,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "every card showing a few live readings and a health score.",
      "startS": 66.745,
      "endS": 69.851,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "It's the hardware view of the site, and any card drills deeper on a click.",
      "startS": 70.294,
      "endS": 74.234,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "Look at the first card.",
      "startS": 74.64,
      "endS": 76.186,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "The point-of-sale is offline.",
      "startS": 77.045,
      "endS": 78.931,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "No health score, no transactions in forty-seven minutes, a red bar flagging it.",
      "startS": 79.188,
      "endS": 84.337,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "When the P-O-S is down the site takes no money, so this is the card you check first.",
      "startS": 85.02,
      "endS": 90.259,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "Sweep the rest.",
      "startS": 90.72,
      "endS": 91.769,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "Conveyor, scanner, chemicals, dryers, water, gate, lighting.",
      "startS": 92.746,
      "endS": 96.993,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "Most run green and healthy; a couple sit lower and earn a second look.",
      "startS": 97.417,
      "endS": 97.885,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "The health number and the color bar do your triage at a glance.",
      "startS": 98.246,
      "endS": 107.433,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "On the right, the open incidents.",
      "startS": 107.9,
      "endS": 109.794,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "Three of them, each tagged by type and, just as usefully, by owner.",
      "startS": 110.266,
      "endS": 114.73,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "The payments outage is on the account manager.",
      "startS": 115.234,
      "endS": 117.462,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "The conveyor stop is still unassigned.",
      "startS": 117.798,
      "endS": 119.921,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "That owner line tells you what already has a name on it and what's waiting for one.",
      "startS": 120.608,
      "endS": 124.8,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "Underneath, the timeline.",
      "startS": 125.2,
      "endS": 126.922,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "Every event with a timestamp, from the shift opening this morning",
      "startS": 127.529,
      "endS": 129.084,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "to the terminal dropping offline later on.",
      "startS": 129.333,
      "endS": 133.246,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "This is the site's story of the day.",
      "startS": 133.537,
      "endS": 135.636,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "When you need to know what led up to an incident, you scroll here.",
      "startS": 136.177,
      "endS": 139.2,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "Bottom right, the quick actions.",
      "startS": 139.6,
      "endS": 141.625,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "The common responses, gathered so you don't go hunting:",
      "startS": 142.402,
      "endS": 145.475,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "raise a work order, book maintenance, send a tech, email the customer, restart the P-O-S.",
      "startS": 145.839,
      "endS": 149.186,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "Every one does something real, so we read the list and stop there.",
      "startS": 149.526,
      "endS": 156.72,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "Step back and take it in.",
      "startS": 157.12,
      "endS": 158.82,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "One page: status up top, then the numbers, the hardware,",
      "startS": 160.186,
      "endS": 160.965,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "the open incidents with owners, the day's history, and the actions that answer them.",
      "startS": 161.66,
      "endS": 164.938,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "Read it top to bottom and you know this site cold,",
      "startS": 165.269,
      "endS": 166.997,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "and you did it without touching a thing.",
      "startS": 167.31,
      "endS": 175.743,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}